    <title>LAN chatroom</title>
    <url>/2019/11/25/LAN-chatroom/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<iframe src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WVjCZBgDepbzkw85w2grPSDVMEgFCST1/preview" width="640" height="480">
</iframe>  
<p style="text-align: center; border-bottom: 0px solid #ddd;"></p>   

<a id="more"></a>  

<h4 id="🌟-Built-with"><a href="#🌟-Built-with" class="headerlink" title="🌟 Built with"></a>🌟 Built with</h4><p>• C</p>
<h4 id="🌟-Components"><a href="#🌟-Components" class="headerlink" title="🌟 Components"></a>🌟 Components</h4><p>Clients:<br>• Send requests to the server and get responses from the server<br>• Multi-threads<br> -detect user’s inputs<br> -receive server’s responses  </p>
<p>Server:<br>• Load and store users’ / sessions’ / invitations’ information<br>• Act as the intermediate between clients<br> -create a new thread for each newly connected client<br> -receive client’s requests and reply responses on every thread  </p>
<h4 id="🌟-Features"><a href="#🌟-Features" class="headerlink" title="🌟 Features"></a>🌟 Features</h4><p>Authentication:<br>• login / logout    </p>
<p>Session (Chatroom):<br>• Users can create a new session or join one existing session<br>• Multiple users can group-chat in one session<br>• Users can join multiple sessions and chat with multiple groups of people<br>• Users can leave the session   </p>
<p>Invitation:<br>• Invite other users to join one existing session<br>• Accept the invitation and join the group chat<br>• Decline the invitation   </p>
<p>Query:<br>• Users can query the list of online users and valid sessions from the server  </p>
<h4 id="📌-Note"><a href="#📌-Note" class="headerlink" title="📌 Note"></a>📌 Note</h4><p>The example ran clients and the server in one same PC thus using 127.0.0.1 as the server IP address.<br>It can be altered as other IP address if the server ran on the different PC.   </p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>C</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>C</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
